snippet.title: Dread X Collection 5 Game Spotlight #2
snippet.description:
A glimpse at 6 of the 12 games for the upcoming Dread X Collection 5. 


Featuring: 
Philisophic Games - Vestige
Roope Tamminen - HUNSVOTTI
Matt Reeves - Beyond the Curtain
PhantomSloth Games - INTERIM
Stroboskop - KARAO
Nikk. F - Spirit Guardian

Wishlist on steam now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1899810/Dread_X_Collection_5/
